snippet.title: HEART ABYSS — Demo Trailer
snippet.description:
Play the demo now — https://store.steampowered.com/app/1892100/HEART_ABYSS/ 

Go deep into unforgiving, brutal, high-speed 2D action filled with a dramatic story of a foxy-eared guy tearing his way out through a ruthless bunch of slavers to save his sister.
